Updated for TCL 9 API change
Large patch due to re-generating SWIG files for a few wrappers (all files ending with "_wrap" suffix).
Also has some manual code fixes to native Tcl plugins, mostly changes from int to Tcl_Size typedef, see files:
tcl_pmepot.c
tcl_fftcmds.c
tcl_sgsmooth.c
tcl_specden.c
tcl_hesstrans.C

